{"tid":1979373,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【萬國時空．沈旭暉 005】 譚德塞可以代表埃塞俄比亞？","createTime":"2020-04-19T11:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T11:26:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c54ec00df609bc0343bb02cf5879010cc0741bc5","tid":1979373,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:22:12.000Z","msg":"【萬國時空．沈旭暉 005】<br />\n譚德塞可以代表埃塞俄比亞？🇪🇹<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SMoZKDre9W8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSMoZKDre9W8&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=840cbbd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SMoZKDre9W8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n70.5K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n【萬國時空．沈旭暉 005】譚德塞可以代表埃塞俄比亞？🇪🇹<br />\n<br />\n之前喺到同大家分享過世衛總幹事譚德塞嘅抗疫表現、喺國際關係中嘅互動，今集就同大家分享譚德塞喺埃塞俄比亞嘅政治角色。作為埃塞俄比亞嘅少數民族－提格雷人（唔係中國人），甚至佢本身唔係喺現今埃塞俄比亞國境內出世（🇪🇷 鄰國厄立特里亞首都阿斯馬拉），佢如何乘住國際關係同國內政治嘅互動，能夠喺政治舞台中上位呢？2018年國內嘅政治變革，執政黨繁榮黨踢走代表示譚德塞民族嘅政黨，又如何影響到譚德塞本人喺抗疫期間，為求鞏固自己地位嘅政治agenda呢？<br />\n<br />\nMusic: Summer - Bensound<br />\n<br />\nSimon 沈旭暉 堅離地 Social Media ▶️ <br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=edb861fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsimon.diplo...&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=7619845a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/simonshen_glos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsimonshen_glos&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=a297271d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/simonshen_glos</a><br />\nBlog: <